130(4): 407&ndash;410. doi:10.1037/com0000043</li>

<li>Ostoji&#263;, Ljerka, Edward W. Legg, Rachael C. Shaw, Lucy G.
Cheke, Michael Mendl, and Nicola S. Clayton, 2014, &ldquo;Can Male
