Female What She Wants?&rdquo;, <em>Biology Letters</em>, 10(3):
20140042. doi:10.1098/rsbl.2014.0042</li>

<li>Palagi, Elisabetta, Alessia Celeghin, Marco Tamietto, Piotr
Winkielman, and Ivan Norscia, 2020, &ldquo;The Neuroethology of
