Mammalian Brains: Do Animals Have Affective Lives?&rdquo;,
<em>Neuroscience &amp; Biobehavioral Reviews</em>, 35(9):
1791&ndash;1804. doi:10.1016/j.neubiorev.2011.08.003</li>

<li>Papadopoulos, Dennis, 2023, &ldquo;Shared Intentionality in
Nonhuman Great Apes: A Normative Model&rdquo;, <em>Review of
Philosophy and Psychology</em>, 14(4): 1125&ndash;1145.
doi:10.1007/s13164-021-00594-x</li>

